<item>
 <title>Happiness: A Visual Poem Exhibit </title>
 <link>http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/node/13205</link>
 <description>
    &lt;p&gt;On view March 3 through 24, 2013, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Happiness: A Visual Poem&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is on exhibit in the Partnership Gallery of the Queens Museum of Art. The event is a celebration of the new International Day of Happiness every year on March 20th, established as a United Nations Resolution in 2012. The exhibit features the poetry of Sri Chinmoy coupled with vivid photographs from countries across the globe. A panel discussion will be held on Sunday March 17th at 1pm and a screening of the film &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Happy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; was held on March 3rd.&lt;/p&gt;


    

    &lt;img src=&quot;http://aum.vasudevaserver.netdna-cdn.com/cdn/farfuture/jlcGbAgW_Yy1pm-B3PD9PmQPWMaIDla_q1rxiizkAhU/mtime:1363145817/files/featured-images/us/img-20130303-00103.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;263&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;    

    &lt;div class=&quot;addressfield-container-inline locality-block country-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;locality&quot; x-autocompletetype=&quot;locality&quot; autocomplete=&quot;locality&quot;&gt;New York&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;country&quot; x-autocompletetype=&quot;country&quot; autocomplete=&quot;country&quot;&gt;United States&lt;/span&gt;    

    &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/art-photography&quot;&gt;Art &amp;amp; Photography&lt;/a&gt;    

    News item    

    On view March 3 through 24, 2013, Happiness: A Visual Poem is on exhibit in the Partnership Gallery of the Queens Museum of Art.     

